data.description: Charming 1 story home in Helotes.  Walk into the perfect open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a study.  Beautiful and modern kitchen with lots of cabinet space and solid countertops.  The extra large master bedroom has enough room for a reading area or even any workout equipment.  Spacious master bath with tub and shower and a walk in closet.  Covered patio leading to backyard perfect for hosting gatherings and for the kids to run and play.   This desirable Bricewood neighborhood gives you the peaceful and quiet feel of country living but only minutes away from city life.  Minutes away from Bandera & 1604 and other shopping centers.  Northside Schools.
